D- Good drinkability that I really enjoy. This is a very coffee forward stout that I would recommend to actual coffee drinkers. The ABV limits this one per say but I would have no problem either having it as a night cap or two of them in a row before going onto something else. 1,340 charactersalleykatking, Feb 14, 2010
