M: Taste evolves and matures nicely. Fairly smooth with a bitter coffee bite.
D: An excellent brew that you want to take your time with in order to properly savor it. Definitely one of the best (if not the best) coffee beer I've come across. And as a coffee lover, I am picky about this. Highly recommended...seek this out! 971 charactersmwilbur, May 06, 2009
