4.42/5  rDev +0.5%look: 4 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.5Pours a somewhat thin black with red edges. Slightly fizzy head that quickly disappears. Smell is of nothing but espresso beans. Taste is very smooth and espresso dominated. Sweetness comes through in the finish, toffee and caramel. There is some chocolate here too, huge and bitter. This is massive!! The alcohol comes through in the end too, once your palate gets used to the espresso taste. Mouthfeel seems a little thin for the amount of dark flavors here. 
